trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of static convenience methods for creating, manipulating, combining, and converting generic vectors.
trans-unit.target: 提供建立、操作、結合以及轉換泛型向量之靜態簡便方法的集合。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns a new vector whose elements are the absolute values of the given vector's elements.
trans-unit.target: 傳回新向量，其元素為指定向量之元素的絕對值。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns a new vector whose values are the sum of each pair of elements from two given vectors.
trans-unit.target: 傳回新的向量，其值為兩個指定向量之每對元素的總和。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns a new vector by performing a bitwise And Not operation on each pair of corresponding elements in two vectors.
trans-unit.target: 透過在兩個向量的每組對應元素上執行位元 And Not 運算，以傳回新的向量。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of unsigned bytes.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成不帶正負號之位元組向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a double-precision floating-point vector.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成雙精確度浮點向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of 16-bit integers.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成 16 位元整數向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of integers.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成整數向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of long integers.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成長整數向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of signed bytes.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成帶正負號之位元組向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a single-precision floating-point vector.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成單精確度浮點向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Reinterprets the bits of a specified vector into those of a vector of unsigned 16-bit integers.
trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成不帶正負號之 16 位元整數向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.

trans-unit.target: 將指定向量的位元轉換成不帶正負號之長整數向量的位元。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns a new vector by performing a bitwise <see langword="And" /> operation on each pair of elements in two vectors.
trans-unit.target: 透過在兩個向量的每對元素上執行位元 <see langword="And" /> 運算，以傳回新的向量。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.

trans-unit.target: 透過在兩個向量的每對元素上執行位元 <see langword="Or" /> 運算，以傳回新的向量。

trans-unit.source: The integral mask vector used to drive selection.
trans-unit.target: 整數遮罩向量，用來選擇磁碟機。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new single-precision vector with elements selected between two specified single-precision source vectors based on an integral mask vector.
trans-unit.target: 依據整數遮罩向量，使用在兩個指定單精確度來源向量之間所選取的元素，來建立新的單精確度向量。

trans-unit.source: The new vector with elements selected based on the mask.

trans-unit.source: The integral mask vector used to drive selection.
trans-unit.target: 整數遮罩向量，用來選擇磁碟機。

trans-unit.source: The new vector with elements selected based on the mask.
trans-unit.target: 使用依據遮照選取之元素的新向量。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns a new vector whose values are the result of dividing the first vector's elements by the corresponding elements in the second vector.
trans-unit.target: 傳回新的向量，其值為第一個向量的元素除以第二個向量之對應元素的結果。

trans-unit.source: <c>T</c> can be any primitive numeric type.
Returns the dot product of two vectors.
Returns a new integral vector whose elements signal whether the elements in two specified double-precision vectors are equal.
trans-unit.target: 傳回新的整數向量，其元素表示兩個指定雙精確度向量的元素是否相等。

Returns a value that indicates whether each pair of elements in the given vectors is equal.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，指出指定向量的每對元素是否相等。
